

{"id":2741,"date":"2023-04-19T11:14:14","date_gmt":"2023-04-19T04:14:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=2741"},"modified":"2023-05-16T14:47:24","modified_gmt":"2023-05-16T07:47:24","slug":"loi-ich-chay-bo-30-phut-moi-ngay","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/loi-ich-chay-bo-30-phut-moi-ngay\/","title":{"rendered":"L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 30 ph\u00fat m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em><strong>l\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, v\u00e0i ph\u00fat ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, ng\u1ee7 ngon h\u01a1n<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 30 ph\u00fat m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? T\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y? L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kho\u1ebb ra sao? Ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft <strong>l\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 30 ph\u00fat m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y\u00a0<\/strong>sau \u0111\u00e2y: <\/span><em><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tim m\u1ea1ch,\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>T\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng ph\u1ea5n ch\u1ea5n,\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Ng\u1ee7 ngon h\u01a1n,\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd.<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><br \/>\nCh\u1ea1y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn; nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau th\u00edch th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u00ean m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 trong nh\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh xa c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t, trong khi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau th\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia \u0111\u1ea1p xe ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 theo \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y h\u00e0ng gi\u1edd li\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <strong>l\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9<\/strong> &#8211; ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 30 ph\u00fat \u0111i b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3374\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3374\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3374 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/loi-ich-cua-viec-chay-bo-1.jpeg\" alt=\"L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, v\u00e0i ph\u00fat ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9,\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/loi-ich-cua-viec-chay-bo-1.jpeg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/loi-ich-cua-viec-chay-bo-1-300x152.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/loi-ich-cua-viec-chay-bo-1-1024x520.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/loi-ich-cua-viec-chay-bo-1-768x390.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/loi-ich-cua-viec-chay-bo-1-1536x780.jpeg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/loi-ich-cua-viec-chay-bo-1-2048x1040.jpeg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3374\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 30 ph\u00fat m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><br \/>\n\u0110I\u1ec0U G\u00cc X\u1ea2Y RA TRONG 30 PH\u00daT CH\u1ea0Y B\u1ed8 C\u1ee6A B\u1ea0N<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><br \/>\nV\u00e0i ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9:<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, n\u0103m ph\u00fat ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi s\u1edbm l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn. C\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ph\u00e2n t\u1eed n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng adenosine triphosphate (ho\u1eb7c ATP) \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 cung c\u1ea5p n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho ch\u00ednh n\u00f3, th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 n\u00f3 thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n. C\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1 tr\u1eef m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ecf nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 n\u00e0y, v\u00ec v\u1eady n\u00f3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ngu\u1ed3n cung c\u1ea5p b\u1ed5 sung &#8211; kh\u00e1 nhanh ch\u00f3ng, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e2n h\u1ee7y glycogen t\u1eeb c\u01a1 v\u00e0 m\u00e1u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qua qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e2n (h\u01a1i th\u1edf).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nh\u00f3m c\u01a1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 quanh v\u00f9ng l\u00f5i, c\u01a1 m\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u00e2n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"><strong>N\u0103m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00fat ti\u1ebfp theo khi ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao kh\u00e1c. Khi b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ea1y, tim c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eadp nhanh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00e1u di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u1eafp c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 nhanh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u0103ng l\u00ean, v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef cho b\u1ea1n m\u00e1t m\u1ebb.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sau m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ph\u00fat ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9:<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e2n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u oxy h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o v\u00e0 glycogen th\u00e0nh n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea5p 15 l\u1ea7n khi b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c, v\u00ec v\u1eady h\u01a1i th\u1edf c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng quen t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y thi\u1ebfu oxy trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, v\u00ec c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. N\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 th\u1edf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"><strong>Ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u quen v\u1edbi c\u00e1c qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfe kho\u1eafn.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi t\u1eadp ch\u1ea1y, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u oxy h\u01a1n m\u1ee9c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cung c\u1ea5p, t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 lactate, ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng oxy. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft lactate v\u1edbi t\u00ean g\u1ecdi kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 axit lactic, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ecfng r\u00e1t m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1edf c\u01a1 b\u1eafp, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chu\u1ed9t r\u00fat, bu\u1ed3n n\u00f4n, c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi chung.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec axit lactic b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00edch t\u1ee5 trong m\u00e1u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nhanh h\u01a1n m\u1ee9c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y n\u00f3 &#8211; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 \u0111ang c\u1ed1 b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i. <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1eadm v\u00e0 t\u0103ng d\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch qua nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng &#8216;ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng lactate&#8217; v\u00e0 t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1eebng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd quen d\u1ea7n khi luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9:<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111i b\u1ed9, hy v\u1ecdng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u01a1 b\u1eafp c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n h\u1ea1 nhi\u1ec7t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i (gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng). Khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, h\u01a1i th\u1edf c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 m\u1eb7t b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ecf b\u1eebng. C\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p cho b\u1ea1n c\u00e1c hormone dopamin c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c hormone endorphin v\u00e0 serotonin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y, s\u1ebd d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 &#8216;c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n&#8217;.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n n\u00ean kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 nhi\u1ec7t sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111i v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><br \/>\nL\u1ee2I \u00cdCH CH\u1ea0Y B\u1ed8 30 PH\u00daT TH\u01af\u1edcNG XUY\u00caN<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><br \/>\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec mong \u0111\u1ee3i trong 30 ph\u00fat ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh khi b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong th\u00f3i quen t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a 30 ph\u00fat ch\u1ea1y ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tim m\u1ea1ch<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u1ea1y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n v\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 nhanh. Trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y xa h\u01a1n ho\u1eb7c nhanh h\u01a1n, v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c oxy \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n. C\u01a1 b\u1eafp c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u quen v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1eddng su\u1ea5t ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u0103ng l\u00ean v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c m\u00ecnh kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3382\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3382\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3382 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cai-thien-suc-khoe-tim-mach-1.jpeg\" alt=\"L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, v\u00e0i ph\u00fat ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9,\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cai-thien-suc-khoe-tim-mach-1.jpeg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cai-thien-suc-khoe-tim-mach-1-300x152.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cai-thien-suc-khoe-tim-mach-1-1024x520.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cai-thien-suc-khoe-tim-mach-1-768x390.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cai-thien-suc-khoe-tim-mach-1-1536x780.jpeg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cai-thien-suc-khoe-tim-mach-1-2048x1040.jpeg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3382\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kho\u1ebb tim m\u1ea1ch<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>T\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng ph\u1ea5n ch\u1ea5n<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng endorphin m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong l\u00fac v\u00e0 ngay sau khi ch\u1ea1y, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f2n h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. C\u00e1c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng 30 ph\u00fat t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u00edch cho c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng tr\u1ea7m c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 lo l\u1eafng, v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y n\u00f3 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tinh th\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3380\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3380\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3380 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-trang-phan-chan-1.jpeg\" alt=\"L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, v\u00e0i ph\u00fat ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9,\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-trang-phan-chan-1.jpeg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-trang-phan-chan-1-300x152.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-trang-phan-chan-1-1024x520.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-trang-phan-chan-1-768x390.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-trang-phan-chan-1-1536x780.jpeg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-trang-phan-chan-1-2048x1040.jpeg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3380\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">T\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng ph\u1ea5n ch\u1ea5n<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Ng\u1ee7 ngon h\u01a1n<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Khi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 ngon h\u01a1n, v\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u00edt c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea5c v\u00e0o ban \u0111\u00eam, v\u00ec hormone g\u00e2y c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng cortisol c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3376\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3376\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3376 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ngu-ngon-hon-1.jpeg\" alt=\"L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, v\u00e0i ph\u00fat ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9,\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ngu-ngon-hon-1.jpeg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ngu-ngon-hon-1-300x152.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ngu-ngon-hon-1-1024x520.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ngu-ngon-hon-1-768x390.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ngu-ngon-hon-1-1536x780.jpeg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ngu-ngon-hon-1-2048x1040.jpeg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3376\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ng\u1ee7 ngon h\u01a1n<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/3-loi-ich-cua-viec-tap-the-duc-hang-ngay\/\">l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y<\/a>, bao g\u1ed3m gi\u1ea3m huy\u1ebft \u00e1p, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tim, kh\u1edbp, c\u01a1 v\u00e0 x\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 m\u1eafc b\u1ec7nh tim, t\u0103ng dung t\u00edch ph\u1ed5i v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, gi\u00fap ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi b\u1ec7nh b\u00e9o ph\u00ec.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3378\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3378\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3378 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cai-thien-tuoi-tho-1.jpg\" alt=\"L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, v\u00e0i ph\u00fat ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9,\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cai-thien-tuoi